{"tid":2381774,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"我登在國安會出文澄清！”戰略耐性“不適用於中國與印太事務！","createTime":"2021-01-26T23:34:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T03:46:22.000Z","uid":28114,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"b37ddcfdb1cf14b42fab1c4c24e0293995bf70e8","tid":2381774,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHyYi2E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHyYi2E.gif&h=b8cb24c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnmXX7R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnmXX7R.jpg&h=e4dea39d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d09c8b309129c776fbfc49a5aff603b97e807f9a","tid":2381774,"uid":389613,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T23:35:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">一早已知 Biden 信唔過，所以我地更應該繼承 Trump 既精神，用 BNO 逼 Biden 同中共開戰</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要有大批香港人離開，會造成現時已經虛弱既經濟徹底崩潰，而中共強行鎖國則引來百國聯軍。<br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">支共反制 BNO 會引致戰爭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[武俠小說] 因為 BNO 香港變成外交博奕戰場！Trump 偷偷地幫香港插左支定海神針迫 Biden 打柒中共！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2377934\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2377934</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">支共比 BNO 走引致經濟崩潰 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/yea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n[神話故事] 中共經濟末日狂奔，BNO 就係大衛與歌利亞決戰粒石頭。港人出走成就 Trump 滅共偉業。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2380593\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2380593</a><br />\n<br />\n--------<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\n不論你係撐 Trump 既手足、定係支持滅共既手足，今次 BNO Visa 係時候身體力行，用你對腳投票去支持 Trump 呢條滅共戰線 </span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300a58096790c2de7418436